snippet.title: Ms Wass,  What Is Your Point? AH & NGN's Answer To Charity Lie
snippet.description:
In this video we talk about Ms Wass and her ridiculous answer to the evidence that AH lied about giving her settlement to the charities.  This is the 2nd video of a series of videos that are going through the transcripts of the UK request for a appeal hearing on March 18, 2021

you can help me with the expenses of attending the VA trial in April 2022 where I will be livestreaming daily and reporting everything that happens daily at the trial by donating to my PayPal account where every dime is solely for this.  donate at TammyTalksAbout/paypal.me While greatly appreciated,  not at all necessary.  thank you for everything you do!
